      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": "大和米蕈（Biobran）",
      "description": "大和米蕈（MGN-3）是大和药品采用独家技术从米糠中研发的健康食品原料，已发表100篇以上研究论文。",
      "url": "https://www.daiwa-pharm.com.cn/videos/biobran/",
      "image": [
        "https://www.daiwa-pharm.com.cn/images/biobran_LENTIN-PLUS-LY-1000_01.png",
        "https://www.daiwa-pharm.com.cn/images/biobran_LENTIN-PLUS-LY-1000_02.png",
        "https://www.daiwa-pharm.com.cn/images/biobran_LENTIN-PLUS-LY-1000_03.png"
      ]
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>